## Animation and Effects

### Starfield Effect

**Location**: `public/script.js`

**Specification**:
- Randomly positioned circles (1-3px diameter)
- 60% of stars blink with random timing
- White base color, yellow blink color
- Density: ~1 star per 10,000 pixels
- Animation duration: 1-4 seconds
- Random delays for natural feel

**Guidelines**:
- Keep animations subtle
- Don't animate too many stars (performance)
- Use CSS animations, not JavaScript loops
- Respect `prefers-reduced-motion`

### Scroll Animations

**Header Collapse**:
- Transition duration: 1s ease
- Elements scale and reposition smoothly
- Flexbox layout shifts

**Hover Effects**:
- Transform: translateX(10px) on feature cards
- Box shadow: subtle yellow glow
- Duration: 0.3s ease
- Never use bounce or elastic easing

### Backdrop Blur

Applied for depth:
- Feature cards: `blur(5px)`
- Section containers: `blur(10px)`
- Footer: `blur(10px)`

**Browser Support**:
```css
/* Include fallback */
.feature {
    background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.05);
    backdrop-filter: blur(5px);
    -webkit-backdrop-filter: blur(5px); /* Safari */
}
```

## Accessibility

### WCAG Standards

**Minimum**: WCAG 2.1 Level AA
**Target**: AAA where feasible

### Color Contrast

**Actual Ratios**:
- Star White (#ffffff) on Night Black (#000000): 21:1 ‚úÖ AAA
- Star Yellow (#fff89a) on Night Black: ~18:1 ‚úÖ AAA
- Muted Text on backgrounds: Minimum 4.5:1 ‚úÖ AA

**Requirements**:
- Normal text: 4.5:1 minimum (AA)
- Large text: 3:1 minimum (AA)
- UI components: 3:1 minimum (AA)

### Semantic HTML

**DO**:
```html
<header>
  <nav>
    <a href="/">Home</a>
  </nav>
</header>
<main>
  <article>
    <h1>Page Title</h1>
    <section>
      <h2>Section Title</h2>
    </section>
  </article>
</main>
<footer>
  <p>&copy; 2025 Ursa Minor Games</p>
</footer>
```

**DON'T**:
```html
<div class="header">
  <div class="nav">
    <span onclick="navigate()">Home</span>
  </div>
</div>
```

### Keyboard Navigation

**Requirements**:
- All interactive elements focusable
- Logical tab order
- Visible focus indicators
- Keyboard shortcuts (optional but nice)
- Skip to content link (for longer pages)

**Focus Styles**:
```css
a:focus,
button:focus {
    outline: 2px solid #fff89a;
    outline-offset: 2px;
}
```

### Screen Reader Support

**ARIA Labels**:
```html
<button aria-label="Open navigation menu">
  <span aria-hidden="true">‚ò∞</span>
</button>

<nav aria-label="Main navigation">
  <!-- nav items -->
</nav>
```

**Alt Text**:
```html
<img src="bear.svg" alt="Ursa Minor Games logo - constellation bear">
```

### Motion Sensitivity

**Respect User Preferences**:
```css
@media (prefers-reduced-motion: reduce) {
    * {
        animation-duration: 0.01ms !important;
        animation-iteration-count: 1 !important;
        transition-duration: 0.01ms !important;
    }
    
    .blink {
        animation: none !important;
    }
}
```

## Responsive Design

### Breakpoints

| Size | Width | Target Devices |
|------|-------|----------------|
| Mobile | < 768px | Phones |
| Tablet | 768px - 1024px | Tablets, small laptops |
| Desktop | > 1024px | Desktops, large laptops |

### Mobile Considerations

**DO**:
- Header scales appropriately (min-height: 64px)
- Touch targets minimum 44x44px
- Readable text without zoom (16px minimum)
- Single column layouts
- Larger interactive elements
- Simplified navigation patterns

**Example**:
```css
@media (max-width: 768px) {
    body {
        font-size: 16px;
    }
    
    h1 {
        font-size: 2rem;
    }
    
    .feature {
        padding: 1.5rem;
    }
    
    header .logo {
        height: 3rem;
    }
}
```

### Desktop Optimization

**Max Content Width**:
```css
main {
