## Performance

### Asset Optimization

**DO**:
- Minimize CSS/JS
- Optimize images
- Use Vite for bundling
- Lazy load non-critical resources
- Cache static assets

**Prefer CSS over Images**:
```css
/* Use gradients instead of image backgrounds */
background: linear-gradient(to bottom, #000000, #002d58);

/* Use CSS shapes instead of images */
.star {
    width: 3px;
    height: 3px;
    border-radius: 50%;
    background: white;
}
```

### Heavy Images

‚ùå **Avoid on homepage**:
- Large background images
- Unoptimized photos
- Multiple high-res images

‚úÖ **Prefer**:
- CSS gradients
- SVG graphics
- Optimized, compressed images
- Lazy loading for below-fold images

